,"dimensions":36},"Tall, regular, narrow letters, v-cut, with small serifs on the termination of strokes. Small deep triangular interpuncts. Alpha has broken bar; epsilon tall, narrow, with equal short horizontals; theta and omicron are rhomboid; mu has vertical first and last, with the diagonals starting below the top and only desencing to the mid-point; nu is similar; rho has small curved, closed loop; sigma is lunate but rectilinear, with very short horizontals.",[37,44],{"type":38,"l":39,"from":40,"to":41,"h":42,"unit":43,"atLeast":42,"atMost":42},"letterHeight","Line 1-2","line1","line2","110","mm",{"type":45,"l":46,"from":40,"to":41,"h":47,"unit":43,"atLeast":47,"atMost":47},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","20",{"_":49,"notBefore":50,"notAfter":51,"evidence":52},"Dated by reference to Flavius Martinianos, consularis of Sicily between 352 and 358 CE (Soraci)",352,358,"prosopography",[54,59],{"_":55,"type":56,"ref":57,"region":58},"Agrigentum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462086","Sicilia",{"_":60,"type":61,"ref":62,"region":58},"Agrigento","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6541860",[64],[65,66],37.32084,13.58876,[68,69],37.297649,13.591579,"Sicily",{"_":72,"role":73,"ref":74},"Parco Archeologico Valle dei Templi","site","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/200",{"type":76},"inventory",{"_":78,"mainLang":79,"languages":80},"Ancient Greek","grc",[78],{"n":82,"url":83,"height":84,"width":85,"desc":26,"surfaceType":86},"screen","ISic001830_tiled.tif","5520px","3680px","front",[88,90],{"atLeast":89,"atMost":89},110,{"atLeast":91,"atMost":91},20,[93],"Caminneci, Parello, Soraci, 2023, Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento",[95],"A7HRWIUH",[97,98,99,15,19,23,100,101,102,103,101,104,105,79],"isic001830","building inscription of martinianos",{"_":12},"agrigentum","agrigento","sicilia","sicily","parco archeologico valle dei templi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-in